
;ホームセンターPAGE2
@ITEM_SHOP_WORK_DETAIL_DEVICE

;アイテム名・価格
PRINTFORML 　《 %ITEMS_ENG(ITEMNAME:SELECT_ITEM)% 》%VALUE_DIGIT(ITEMPRICE:SELECT_ITEM)%G 
SELECTCASE ITEMNAME:SELECT_ITEM
CASE "業務用魔力貯蔵器"
	PRINTL ＜Upgrade＞
	PRINTFORML Increases Mana storage capacity to %VALUE_DIGIT(MAGIC_TANK_BUSINESSUSE)%MP.
	PRINTL
	PRINTL A device that stores Mana and can be used as a battery, for business use.
	PRINTL In the demon world, "machines" operate using Mana, but there are many humans who either lack Mana
	PRINTL or cannot recover enough Mana in a single day to operate the machines,
	PRINTL so a battery for operating the machines is very important.
	PRINTL
	PRINTL That said, for regular use, the amount of Mana in what we would call a "battery" in our world
	PRINTL is sufficient, so it is not typically used in the form of a Mana storage device.
	
CASE "大容量魔力貯蔵器"
	PRINTL ＜Unlock＞
	PRINTFORML Increases Mana storage capacity to %VALUE_DIGIT(MAGIC_TANK_LARGE_CAPACITY)%MP.
	PRINTL
	PRINTL A device that stores Mana and can be used as a battery, reinfocred version.
	IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
		PRINTL An at-any-cost high-end model that boasts an enormous storage capacity. 
		PRINTL It took the elite members of the Demon King's Army, 
		PRINTL including the Demon King himself, several days to fill up this reservoir.
	ENDIF
	
CASE "スタイリング道具セット"
	PRINTL ＜Unlock＞
	PRINTL Visit → Change Hairstyle
	PRINTL
	PRINTL A set of tools needed to arrange a girl's hair.
	PRINTL While scissors are enough for men's hair, girls' hair is delicate, so various tools are required.
	PRINTL Comes with a guide that even beginners can understand.
	IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
		PRINTL
		PRINTL While cutting hair is one thing, this mysterious set can instantly change short hair to long hair.
		PRINTL Perhaps it contains some kind of magic that makes it possible.
	ENDIF
	
CASE "工具セット"
	PRINTL ＜Unlock＞
	PRINTL Development/Learning → Development of New-Model Milking Machine
	PRINTL
	PRINTL A complete set of tools needed to build or modify machines.
	PRINTL とはいえ巨大な機械を作れるほどではないので、搾乳器を開発するために使う。
	PRINTL Comes with a guide that even beginners can understand。
	
CASE "裁縫道具セット"
	PRINTL ＜Unlock＞
	PRINTL Visit → Repair Torn Clothes
	PRINTL
	PRINTL A set of tools needed to repair torn clothing.
	PRINTL Comes with a guide that even beginners can understand。
	

;外れたんだけど一応ここに残しておく
CASE "ネクロノミコン"
    PRINTL ＜Unlock＞
    PRINTL Development/Learning → Magic Acquisition
    PRINTL
    PRINTL A reference needed to learn magic.
    PRINTL The ＜Al Azif＞ grimoire, containing almost every form of magic from the demon world,
    PRINTL has been condensed to exclude spells that lack clear principles, are too advanced to be practically acquired,
    PRINTL or are overly niche, thus keeping the volume manageable.
    IF FLAG:ジョーク表示
        PRINTL
        PRINTL Though an extraordinary artifact for humans on the surface, often sparking deadly conflicts,
        PRINTL in the demon world, it's simply a reference book anyone can buy, price notwithstanding, at the bookstore.
	ENDIF
	
CASE "マジカル裁ちバサミ"
	PRINTL ＜Unlock＞
	PRINTL Clothing Modification → Altered to Increase Exposure
	PRINTL
	PRINTL Allows modifying compatible clothing to increase exposure.
ENDSELECT


